      "content": "In the Midstream EBITDA breakdown for Equinor, the data reveals significant financial metrics across three critical categories as of December 2023. The first category, Transportation, contributes a substantial amount of $50M, showcasing the importance of this segment in the overall operations. Following closely, the Processing category generates $30M, which highlights its role in the value chain. The third category, Storage, records an essential contribution of $20M, rounding out the operational performance across these segments. The cumulative effect of these contributions leads to a TotalEBITDA of $100M, reflecting robust profitability metrics.",
